OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FCampaigners and politicians have been
OL,8,Fsharing their reactions to Jersey's
OL,9,Flandmark decision to pass its assisted
OL,10,Fdying legislation.
OL,12,FThe momentous vote - supported by two-
OL,13,Fthirds of politicians - would allow a
OL,14,Fterminally ill person who has been a
OL,15,FJersey resident for at least a year
OL,16,Fand is experiencing, or expected to
OL,17,Fexperience, "unbearable suffering" a
OL,18,Fchoice to end their life with the help
OL,19,Fof a willing medical professional.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FThey must have less than six months to
OL,8,Flive, or 12 months if they have a
OL,9,Fneurodegenerative condition such as
OL,10,FMotor Neurone Disease, and the
OL,11,Flegislation will not become law until
OL,12,Fit is given Royal Assent.
OL,14,FThere is also a legal process with a
OL,15,Fminimum time period from the first
OL,16,Fexpression for an assisted death to it
OL,17,Fbeing carried out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FTwo independent doctors have to agree,
OL,8,Fthere is a court appeals process for
OL,9,Fthose with a "special interest", and
OL,10,Fthe person must give their free and
OL,11,Finformed consent.
OL,13,FWhile some say the bill "shortens
OL,14,Fneedless suffering", others argue it
OL,15,Fessentially legalises "assisted
OL,16,Fsuicide".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FLorna Pirozzolo, who has incurable
OL,8,Fbreast cancer and is in favour of the
OL,9,Flaw change, explains: "We've been so
OL,10,Fclear that it is not life and death;
OL,11,Fthese people are dying, their body is
OL,12,Fin an irreversible state of dying,
OL,13,Fthey can't be brought back from that.
OL,15,F"This is literally just about
OL,16,Fshortening that so they are not
OL,17,Fneedlessly suffering."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FShe adds: "It is amazing just to know
OL,8,Fthat whatever happens, and if things
OL,9,Fstart to decline more quickly than we
OL,10,Fthought, then I don't have to worry."
OL,12,FLorna says former ITV Channel
OL,13,Fjournalist, Gary Burgess, and
OL,14,Fhumanitarian aid worker Simon Boas
OL,15,Finspired her to continue fighting for
OL,16,Fthe right to choose.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FShe explains: "I got to know them
OL,8,Fmonths before they died, and both of
OL,9,Fthem just said, 'What you are doing is
OL,10,Fgreat and please keep it up', so
OL,11,Freally that's what's kept me going.
OL,13,F"It is tough, and it's taken a real
OL,14,Ftoll on me, but they have kept me
OL,15,Fgoing, and I wish they were here to
OL,16,Fsee it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"Like so many terminally ill people
OL,8,FI've spoken with, I'm not scared of
OL,9,Fdying, but I am terrified of suffering
OL,10,Fas I go. That's why this law is so
OL,11,Fbadly needed.
OL,13,F"No one should have to endure
OL,14,Funbearable pain at the end of their
OL,15,Flife, or feel they have to leave their
OL,16,Fhome or their loved ones behind to
OL,17,Fhave control."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FSarah Wootton, Chief Executive of the
OL,8,Fpro campaign group 'Dignity in Dying',
OL,9,Fsays: "Compassion has won out in
OL,10,FJersey, in a week that demonstrates
OL,11,Fundeniable momentum for change right
OL,12,Facross the UK and Crown Dependencies.
OL,13,FToday's historic result will bring
OL,14,Fprofound relief to so many.
OL,16,F"It is a testament to the families who
OL,17,Fhave tirelessly pushed for change, and
OL,18,Fto the States Assembly, which listened.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"This progress is proof of the humble
OL,8,Ftenacity of dying people, families and
OL,9,Fthe wider public, who simply will not
OL,10,Fgive up until their Parliament acts.
OL,11,FThe time for choice and compassion on
OL,12,Four shores has well and truly arrived."
OL,14,FJersey's Chief Minister, Deputy Lyndon
OL,15,FFarnham, says: "This has been a long,
OL,16,Fcareful and considered journey, and I
OL,17,Fwant to commend the Assembly for the
OL,18,Frespectful way in which the debate was
OL,19,Fconducted.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"I think many members feel more
OL,8,Fconfident now in the depth and the
OL,9,Fquality of the legislation we have in
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,F"But of course this isn't the end of
OL,13,Fit, it's the beginning, and we need to
OL,14,Fmake sure that we monitor, that we
OL,15,Fthink carefully and have very careful
OL,16,Fregulation."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FThe Chair of Jersey's Assisted Dying
OL,8,FReview Panel, Deputy Louise Doublet,
OL,9,Fadds: "I am really relieved we have
OL,10,Fgot to this stage, and I am really
OL,11,Fpleased for anyone who has suffered in
OL,12,Fthe future and might be able to access
OL,13,Fthis and have that suffering eased."
OL,15,FJersey resident David Delauney
OL,16,Fsupports the law change after his
OL,17,Fpersonal experience, explaining: "My
OL,18,Fsister never wanted to be in the
OL,19,Fhospital, and she ended up in the
OL,20,Fhospital and had three miserable years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G11/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"My sister said to me, 'This is no
OL,8,Flife,' and she wanted to die, she
OL,9,Fwanted to die for about four or five
OL,10,Fyears; it's worse than people think.
OL,12,F"I think it was definitely the right
OL,13,Fchoice. I think you have a choice over
OL,14,Fyour life. It is your life."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FHowever, others raise serious
OL,8,Fsafeguarding concerns, especially
OL,9,Fregarding vulnerable people, and worry
OL,10,Fthat this law change will start a
OL,11,F'slippery slope' where politicians
OL,12,Fwill gradually widen the criteria for
OL,13,Fan assisted death.
OL,15,FThe campaign group 'Care Not Killing'
OL,16,Fhas criticised the bill, labelling the
OL,17,Flegislation "assisted suicide".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G13/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,FIts Chief Executive Officer, Dr Gordon
OL,8,FMacdonald, says: "Before the Health
OL,9,FMinister, Deputy Tom Binet, does a
OL,10,Fvictory lap for legalising assisted
OL,11,Fsuicide and euthanasia in Jersey, he
OL,12,Fwould do well to remember that the
OL,13,FBill faces many challenges, not least
OL,14,Fto ask, does it protect the
OL,15,Fvulnerable, disabled people and those
OL,16,Fat risk of being coerced?
OL,18,F"Given the lengthy delay we have seen
OL,19,Fwith a less permissive Bill from the
OL,20,FIsle of Man, the answer seems to be
OL,21,F'highly unlikely'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G14/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"When matters as sensitive and life-
OL,8,Faltering as assisted dying are brought
OL,9,Fbefore a legislative body, there is a
OL,10,Fclear requirement to protect
OL,11,Fvulnerable people; in some cases, this
OL,12,Fmeans treating them differently to
OL,13,Fensure that they are not pressured
OL,14,Finto ending their lives.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G15/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38216
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"There are also significant unanswered
OL,8,Fquestions with the Bill as to how it
OL,9,Fwill operate with many doctors,
OL,10,Fincluding those who visit the island
OL,11,Fto provide specialist services,
OL,12,Findicating that they do not want to be
OL,13,Finvolved in killing their patients."
OL,15,FDr Macdonald concludes: "We need to
OL,16,Fcare for people who are suffering, not
OL,17,Fencourage them or provide them with a
OL,18,Fmechanism to end their lives.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G16/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"This is why we champion the extension
OL,8,Fof high-quality palliative care to all
OL,9,Fthose who need it and better support
OL,10,Ffor their families.
OL,12,F"This is the real progressive agenda,
OL,13,Fand why we argue for care not killing."
OL,15,FEchoing the criticism, Deputy Phillip
OL,16,FBailache, a member of the Assisted
OL,17,FDying Review Panel, says: "My
OL,18,Freaction, of course, is disappointment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G17/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"I am not in favour of assisted dying,
OL,8,FI am all in favour of compassion, I am
OL,9,Fin favour of people having deaths
OL,10,Fwhich are good deaths, but I am not in
OL,11,Ffavour of the law which has just been
OL,12,Fpassed.
OL,14,F"Life is a precious thing, and I don't
OL,15,Fthink really it is for people to
OL,16,Fremove life, in the way in which the
OL,17,Fassisted dying law is now going to
OL,18,Fauthorise.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G18/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38219
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1772209190
OL,3,CAssisted dying vote reaction:
OL,4,C'Shortening suffering' or 'assisted
OL,5,Csuicide'?
OL,7,F"I think there are very deep ethical
OL,8,Fissues in this subject, and I fear it
OL,9,Fwill change the community of Jersey in
OL,10,Fa way that we cannot foresee."
OL,12,FJersey's Health Minister, Deputy Tom
OL,13,FBinet, says he is "very happy and
OL,14,Fpleased" with the outcome, but
OL,15,F"respects the views of everyone".
OL,17,FHe adds: "There will be a celebration
OL,18,Ffrom a lot of people ... but there
OL,19,Fwill be a lot of people upset and
OL,20,Fdisturbed by it."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G19/19
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
